### 建立報名
POST http://localhost:3000/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "0987654321",
  "status": "pending"
}

### 再次用同 email 報名（預期要 400）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Duplicate User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "0911111111",
  "status": "pending"
}

### 查詢報名（含分頁測試）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/signup?page=1&limit=5

### 更新 phone / status
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/signup/6932dfa9a5a018edf2363c34
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "0912345678",
  "status": "confirmed"
}

### 刪除報名
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/signup/6932dfa9a5a018edf2363c34

